I"Õ<p>This value set includes codes from <a href="http://tools.ietf.org/html/bcp47">BCP-47</a>. This value set matches the ONC 2015 Edition LanguageCommunication data element value set within C-CDA to use a 2 character language code if one exists,   and a 3 character code if a 2 character code does not exist. It points back to <a href="https://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc5646">RFC 5646</a>, however only the language codes are required, all other elements are optional.</p>
